channel.title: Dont judge people by there rep!
channel.description: Well look at my rep its in the 50's.But im still stupid! Like + saint + Every judged him cause he only had 10 rep. But the hidden thing was he has been reading for ages. As a guest,reading,reading etc.... He tought hisself by looking at others mistakes and ways people fix and do things. Tbh he's a smart guy. But he only has 10 rep -.- SO dont just judge peeps by rep!
